'''Large Goat Milk''' (called '''L. Goat Milk''' in-game) is an [[:Category:Animal Products|animal product]] obtained from a [[Goat]] with sufficient [[Animals#Animal Care|friendship and mood]]. It can also randomly rotate into the [[Traveling Cart]]'s stock for {{tprice|345}}.

==Gifting==
{{GiftsByItem
|like=Robin,Linus,Pierre,Evelyn,Penny,Pam,Jodi,Leah,Marnie,Harvey,Sandy
