|dislike=Lewis,Haley,Elliott,Dwarf,Wizard
|hate=Kent
}}

==Bundles==
*Large Goat Milk is an option for the {{Bundle|Animal||y}}.
*Ten Milk (any size, including [[Goat Milk]] and Large Goat Milk) may be required for the {{Bundle|home cook||y}}.

==Artisan Goods==
:''See also: [[Animal Products Profitability]]''
Goat Milk can be used to make the following [[Artisan Goods]].  Note that regular [[Goat Milk]] always produces regular quality [[Goat Cheese]], while Large Goat Milk always produces gold-quality [[Goat Cheese]].  The quality of the milk is not a factor.

Goat Cheese may be aged in [[Cask]]s to increase its quality.
