==Recipes==
{{#lsth:Milk|Recipes}}

==Tailoring==
Large Goat Milk is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt025|link=Tailoring{{!}}Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a white dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed.

==Quests==
Large Goat Milk is not used in any [[Quests|quests]].

